'''Candy Quest 2025''' is an event centered around [[Special:MyLanguage/Spookality 2025|Spookality 2025]]. Collect candy from other users' companions, to fill out the Candy Codex, and earn the Candy Codex Completionist [[Special:MyLanguage/Badges|badge]].

[[File:Candy_Quest_2025_Header.webp|1000px|thumb|right|Header Image from official blog post]]

== Items ==
There are both free items, and optional items for Candy Quest that require [[VRC Credits|VRC Credits]] ({{Credits}}). 

Participating in the event does not require any purchases, however, acquiring companions - Kath and Treats - can help other users complete their Candy Codex.

