===Candy Codex===
[[File:Candy Codex - Item from Spookality 2025.png|thumb|100x100px|The Candy Codex]]
The Candy Codex is an [[Special:MyLanguage/Items|item]] that can be redeemed for free from the [[Special:MyLanguage/Shop|Shop]]<ref name=":0">[https://help.vrchat.com/hc/en-us/articles/45472973853075-Candy-Quest-FAQ "Candy Quest FAQ"] on ''[[ask.vrchat.com]]''. Dated October 14, 2025. Retrieved October 15, 2025.</ref>. It serves as a log book to keep track of your collected candy<ref name=":0" />.

The Candy Codex has 8 slots, 4 for wrapped candies and 4 for lollipops<ref name=":0" />. Once you fill your Candy Codex, you will no longer be able to collect more candy, and will receive the Candy Codex Completionist badge<ref name=":0" />.

Candy can be collected from other users Treats and Kath companions after waiting for a short time. When a companion is ready to have its candy collected, it will glow and present the candy in front of itself<ref name=":0" />. Clicking the companion collects the candy. You must have your Candy Codex out for companions to present you with candy.

Each companion produces a unique piece of candy with theming that matches the companions unique attributes (Treats' wings and Kaths' antennae)<ref name=":0" />. Once you have collected candy from a companion, you are not able to collect candy from that same companion again<ref name=":0" />.

===Companions===
There are two custom companions available for Candy Quest and Spookality 2025: Kath, and Treats.
==== Kath ====
[[File:Kath - Companion Item from Spookality 2025.png|thumb|100x100px|Kath, a Spookality Companion]]
Kath is an analog CRT monitor companion, with a glowing yellow jagged face. Kath companions can be given a custom color palette by their owner, by going to the [[Inventory]] tab in the [[Main Menu]], clicking the Cosmetics section, and selecting "Customize Palette".
Kath will beep, when pet by their owner, or by another user. Each Kath companion will make a lollipop candy for the Candy Codex.

==== Treats ====
[[File:Treats - Companion Item from Spookality 2025.png|thumb|100x100px|Treats, a Spookality Companion]]
Treats is a white feline-like companion with stubby paws, and bat-like wings. All Treats companions have a unique set of colors, and patterns on their wings that are different for every owner.
Treats will purr, when pet by their owner, or by another user. Each Treats companion will make tube-shaped candy for the Candy Codex, which will be the same color and pattern as their wings.

===Candy Codex Completionist badge===
[[File:Candy_Codex_Completionist.png|thumb|100x100px|The "Candy Codex Completionist" badge]]
Users who obtain every candy necessary for filling in the Candy Codex, will receive that Candy Codex Completionist [[Special:MyLanguage/Badges|badge]] for their profile. This badge is an orange [[wikipedia:Jack-O-Lantern|jack-o-lantern]] bucket, filled with various candies. The description of the badge is as follows:
<blockquote>''"Awarded to those that were able to complete their Candy Codex during Spookality 2025"</blockquote>

